  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Distributes 440,000 liters of gas in 5 days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Litro Gas Company has distributed 440,000 domestic gas cylinders in the five days from last 11th to today (15th), said Litro Gas Company's media spokesperson V. Mr. Keteswaram said today (15).",
        "Mr. Keteswaram said that 80,000 to 100,000 domestic gas cylinders are to be released today and he also mentioned that the gas supply will continue.",
        "After almost 40 days, Litro Gas Company started the gas supply from Colombo city limits on the 11th and the gas distribution is currently in operation all over Sri Lanka."
      ],
